  "text": "We also tested whether YY1 affects AKT dephosphorylation in two in vitro dephosphorylation assays [CITATION_1] . Dephosphorylation of AKT S473 and T308 is mediated by two phosphatases, PHLPP2 and PP2A, respectively. As presented in Supplementary Figure S6A -C, YY1 does not change the kinetics of AKT dephosphorylation at S473 and T308.",
